<description>THE NATIONAL WEATHER SERVICE HAS EXTENDED SEVERE THUNDERSTORM
WATCH 460 TO INCLUDE THE FOLLOWING AREAS UNTIL 7 PM EDT THIS
EVENING
IN CONNECTICUT THIS WATCH INCLUDES 1 COUNTY
IN NORTHWESTERN CONNECTICUT
LITCHFIELD
IN MASSACHUSETTS THIS WATCH INCLUDES 1 COUNTY
IN WESTERN MASSACHUSETTS
BERKSHIRE
IN NEW YORK THIS WATCH INCLUDES 1 COUNTY
IN EAST CENTRAL NEW YORK
DUTCHESS
THIS INCLUDES THE CITIES OF ARLINGTON, BEACON, DALTON, FLORIDA,
HANCOCK, NORTH ADAMS, PITTSFIELD, POUGHKEEPSIE, AND TORRINGTON.</description>
